text: Kanjwani railway station (, ) is a railway station which is found in Tehsil Tandlianwala , Punjab, Pakistan. ==See also== * List of railway stations in Pakistan * Pakistan Railways ==References== ==External links== *Official Web Site of Pakistan Railways Category:Railway stations in Faisalabad District Category:Railway stations on Shorkot–Sheikhupura line
